# A [[fairground]] [[attraction]] in which participants ride through a "haunted house" in a [[railcar]].
# {{theater}} An excursion done by many [[tourist]] [[railway]]s around the world.  Usually, a [[fiction]]al story is created and performed with static displays or live actors on either side of a train.  [[actor|Actor]]s and [[actresses]] play out a story on the long and narrow stage provided by the [[railcar]] [[aisles]].

